  m_Name: perch-day1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  characterName: Perch
  characterPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 294e71e358c2dfb45b5c51fb16a10c47, type: 3}
  lines:
  - JEESSUUUS CHRIST AND THE REST OF THE HOLY FAMILY!
  - WHY BRING ME THIS UGLY, FILTHY, STINKY PIECE OF SHIT?
  - YOU REMIND ME OF THAT LOUD LITTLE BOY TEDDY.
  - AND WHERE IS THAT LOUD LITTLE PRICK NOW?
  - CERTAINLY NOT WITH JEESSUUUS CHRIST AND THE REST OF THE HOLY FAMILY. THATS FOR
    SURE.
  - NOW IF YOU WANT TO STAY IN OUR COMFORTABLE LITTLE TOWN. THERE ARE A FEW RULES.
  - '1: YOU HAVE TO MEET MY DAILY QUOTA!'
  - YOU CAN CHECK YOUR QUOTA FOR THE DAY BY TALKING TO ME AND LOOKING AT MY SHOP.
  - 'WE WERE ONCE A BUZZING TOWN YOU KNOW. '
  - SO WE NEED YOUR UGLY MUG TO PROVIDE FOR US TOO.
  - IF YOU WANT TO CONTINUE RECEIVING OUR WARM HOSPITALITY.
  - '4: MEET OUR QUOTA BEFORE 10PM EVERY NIGHT!'
  - TRUST ME, YOU REALLY DONT WANT TO MISS THE QUOTA.
  - '10: IGNORE THE NOISES YOU HEAR UPSTAIRS!'
  - MY PETS ARE POORLY TRAINED. THEY MISBEHAVE TOO OFTEN.
  - '2: DO NOT MISS YOUR QUOTA... '
  - GO TO THE END OF THE DOCK AND GET TO WORK.
  - NOW GET YOUR DISGUSTING WHITE PASTY ASS OUT OF MY SHOP!
  textSpeed: 35
  typingSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f5d143911732a1f43b570748ed2458a4, type: 3}
